Amedya : Wi ibγan a d iẓuṛ iṛuḥ

Wi ibγan a d iẓuṛ iṛuḥ
Izger lebḥeṛ di ccetwa

Isafen iγeẓṛan γur-s
Dinna a y teqwa lbaṛaka

Lǧennet a syadi tewɛaṛ
Deffir laɛtiba ay tella



